y, but no prior knowledge, fail to\nconverge and generalize poorly on CFGs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 7 Sep 2019 00:32:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2019 20:12:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-23"}
